name: Domainspike
overview:
Domainspike provides a genuine mass development solution with the simplicity of a parking solution and the power of a content management system.

It is designed for domain owners who want to improve the financial returns on their domain portfolios through scalable development, optimization and management.

Domainspike leverages keyword intelligence and search data to deliver unique, targeted and useful content rich websites and provides actionable performance analysis. Domainspike is powered by Parklings, which has built over 170,000 websites in less than 12 months.

Domainspike will be unveiled at Domainfest in Santa Monica 2nd February, 2011 and launched in beta early March, 2011.
